# Testing

- Focus critical paths; ~30-40% coverage.
- Test: security/auth/validation, core logic, critical APIs, data integrity.
- Skip: simple UI, trivial code, type defs, wrappers, config, basic CRUD.
- Keep fast/deterministic; test behavior; integration for APIs, mock externals.
